content.rendered:
Directed by Advait Chandan.

Written by Advait Chandan.

Cast Zaira Wasim(Insia). Meher Vij(Najma). Raj Arjun(Farookh). Aamir Khan(Shakti Kumar). Tirth Sharma(Chintan). Kabir Sajid Shaikh(Guddu (as Kabir Sajid)). Farrukh Jaffar(Badi Apa). Manuj Sharma(Ranjeet). Nikita Anand(Sheetal Mam). Shaan(Self). Monali Thakur(Self). Mona Ambegaonkar(Sheena Sabhawala). Jasmeet Singh Bhatia(Cheesy News Anchor Host). Dianne Commissariat(Sheena’s Receptionist). Patrali Chattopadhyay(Glamour Awards Girl). Fatima Ashraf(Insia’s Friend Mansi).Jasleen Singh. Sheblu Ahmed(Ron). Fahad Dayee(Sanjay). Md Shohag Hossain(Insia’s Classmate). Tony Ji(Youtuber). Musa Muhammed Olayinka(Najma Brother). Umair Patel(Playback singer (archive sound))

Language Hindi.

Producers Akash Chawla. Aamir Khan. Sujay Kutty. Allen Liu. Girish Patel. B. Shrinivas Rao. Kiran Rao. Prasad Shetty.

Production Aamir Khan Production. E Stars Film.
